<HL>
   Politics &amp; Policy:
   GAO Is Unable
   To See Extent
   Of Corn Toxin
   ----
   By Scott Kilman
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/03/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A22
</SO>
<IN>
